author: arkurth
msg: Changed timeout value in OS.pm::is_ssh_responding from 15 to 30 seconds. Changed value in Windows.pm::user_logged_in to 60 seconds.
Updated Windows.pm::post_load to only call logoff_users if wait_for_logoff returns false.
Removed unnecessary call to is_ssh_responding from get_system32_path.
Added check for a warning that is displayed if PAE is enabled in disable_hibernation.
